column2: The Orders of sentence contained in pages 06 and 07 of the impugned order of the
High Court Judge dated 29th November 2019 are hereby vacated and set aside.
The  learned  Judge  of  the  High  Court  is  directed  to  hear  both  counsel  for  the
Appellant  and  the  Respondent  and  make  a  fresh  lawful  order  regarding  the
sentence imposed by the learned Magistrate.
